Title: Fix double slashes in tmpfs fstab entries
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: omd
Date: 1607071275
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0b2

Previous 2.0.0 releases create tmpfs entries in /etc/fstab with double slashes
in the path (e.g. "/opt//omd/sites/beta/tmp"). The paths are now correcltly
using a single slash as separator.
